Sentencas: The electrochemical characteristics and product distribution for a ceria-based solid oxide fuel cell using hydrogen sulfide as the fuel were examined.
Titulo: Utilization of hydrogen sulfide in an intermediate-temperature ceria-based solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The cell studied had the configuration H2S, Pt\(CeO2)(0.8)(SmO1.5)\Pt, air.
Titulo: Utilization of hydrogen sulfide in an intermediate-temperature ceria-based solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Low anode over-potentials and high exchange current densities (>60 mA/cm(2) in some instances) were observed.
Titulo: Utilization of hydrogen sulfide in an intermediate-temperature ceria-based solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: An analysis of the product distribution showed that complete oxidation of hydrogen sulfide to sulfur dioxide las opposed to sulfur) and water appears to be the favored reaction pathway.
Titulo: Utilization of hydrogen sulfide in an intermediate-temperature ceria-based solid oxide fuel cell
